00:32:52.291 --> 00:32:54.032
AW, SUSAN,
THAT'S GREAT.


702
00:32:54.075 --> 00:32:57.252
I MEAN, THE MINUTE
I SAW YOU, MY HEART
WAS JUST LIKE...


703
00:32:57.296 --> 00:33:00.125
