RIGHT NOW.


786
00:38:48.647 --> 00:38:49.474
OH, YEAH.

787
00:38:55.131 --> 00:38:56.698
THIS RIGGING'S
TOO LOOSE.


788
00:38:56.742 --> 00:38:59.266
ALL THIS JIBING'S
GONNA SNAP A MAST.


789
00:38:59.309 --> 00:39:01.399
ROLL IN THE JIB
AND TAKE DOWN
HALF THE MAIN.


790
00:39:01.442 --> 00:39:02.487
YEAH.

791
00:39:10.799 --> 00:39:14.455
GOD, I HATE
THIS STUPID RIG.


792
00:39:14.499 --> 00:39:15.891
WE NEED SOME HELP.

793
00:39:18.024 --> 00:39:20.896
I GUESS YOU SHOULD
GO GET MATT.


794
00:39:20.940 --> 00:39:22.115
GO.

795
00:39:25.292 --> 00:39:27.425
MATT, WAKE UP.

796
00:39:27.468 --> 00:39:29.209
COME ON, WAKE UP.

797
00:39:29.252 --> 00:39:31.167
I THINK
HE PASSED OUT.


798
00:39:31.211 --> 00:39:34.388
PERFECT. WE'RE UP THERE
FIGHTING A GALE,
AND HE'S DRINKING?


799
00:39:34.432 --> 00:39:36.085
IT'S PRETTY
ROUGH OUT, ISN'T IT?


800
00:39:36.129 --> 00:39:39.175
HOW WOULD YOU KNOW?
YOU'VE BEEN DOWN HERE
ALL NIGHT.


801
00:39:39.219 --> 00:39:40.786
LOOK, I DIDN'T
MEAN IT, OK?


802
00:39:40.829 --> 00:39:42.831
I'M JUST WIPED OUT.

803
00:39:42.875 --> 00:39:44.572
AAH!

804
00:39:44.616 --> 00:39:45.965
YOU OK?

805
00:39:46.008 --> 00:39:47.183
YEAH.

806
00:39:47.227 --> 00:39:48.184
MAN,
WHAT'S GOING ON?


807
00:39:48.228 --> 00:39:51.013
WE NEED YOUR HELP
UP ON DECK.


808
00:39:51.057 --> 00:39:53.146
