809
00:39:53.189 --> 00:39:54.713
GIVE ME A CLUE,
MATT.


810
00:39:54.756 --> 00:39:55.844
YOU GONNA BE
A JERK ALL NIGHT,


811
00:39:55.888 --> 00:39:57.193
