817
00:40:04.157 --> 00:40:05.811
OK.

818
00:40:12.600 --> 00:40:15.037
ALLIE,
PUT SOME GEAR ON.


819
00:40:17.910 --> 00:40:18.954
TAKE IT DOWN.

820
00:40:18.998 --> 00:40:20.303
I'M GONNA
REDUCE THE SAIL.


821
00:40:20.347 --> 00:40:22.262
OK. FASTEN
YOUR SAFETY LINE.


822
00:40:35.014 --> 00:40:37.799
I'M TRYING
TO REEF THE MAIN,
BUT IT'S BOUND OFF!


823
00:40:37.843 --> 00:40:38.800
RICK!

824
00:40:38.844 --> 00:40:40.149
OHH!

825
00:40:40.193 --> 00:40:42.630
RICK, HANG ON!
HANG ON, RICK!


826
00:40:46.895 --> 00:40:49.115
RICK, ARE YOU OK?

827
00:40:49.158 --> 00:40:51.030
I'M ALL RIGHT!

828
00:40:51.073 --> 00:40:52.118
ALLIE, WHAT
ARE YOU DOING?


829
00:40:52.161 --> 00:40:53.467
I WANT TO HELP.

830
00:40:53.511 --> 00:40:55.338
IT'S TOO DANGEROUS.
GET BELOW.


831
00:40:55.382 --> 00:40:56.557
NO.

832
00:40:59.212 --> 00:41:01.214
[MUTTERING]

833
00:41:05.000 --> 00:41:07.699
FAR ENOUGH!
HOLD IT THERE!


834
00:41:11.485 --> 00:41:12.660
HOLD ON!

835
00:41:15.576 --> 00:41:16.621
JASON!

836
00:41:21.887 --> 00:41:23.845
Susan:
JASON, ARE YOU HURT?


837
00:41:23.889 --> 00:41:25.673
NO, I'M...
I'M ALL RIGHT.


838
00:41:26.805 --> 00:41:28.546
NEED HELP
ON THE STERN.


839
00:41:28.589 --> 00:41:31.723
MAKE SURE YOU FASTEN
YOUR SAFETY LINE.


840
00:41:31.766 --> 00:41:34.900
SECURE THE LINES
AND CLEAR THE DECK!


841
00:41:34.943 --> 00:41:36.031
OK!

842
00:41:42.690 --> 00:41:43.778
AAH!

843
00:41:45.475 --> 00:41:46.389
OHH!

844
00:41:46.433 --> 00:41:48.087
ALLIE!

845
00:41:48.130 --> 00:41:49.175
RICK!

846
00:41:50.872 --> 00:41:54.006
RICK, ALLIE'S HURT!
SHE'S ON THE STERN!


847
00:41:54.049 --> 00:41:55.442
OK, I'M COMING!

848
00:42:01.970 --> 00:42:03.319
ALLIE, I'M HERE.

849
00:42:03.363 --> 00:42:04.364
YOU OK?

850
00:42:04.407 --> 00:42:07.497
BABY, WHAT HAPPENED?

851
00:42:07.541 --> 00:42:09.674
I WAS TRYING TO HELP.

852
00:42:09.717 --> 00:42:11.284
YOU SHOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN UP HERE.


853
00:42:11.327 --> 00:42:13.068
I KNOW.

854
00:42:13.112 --> 00:42:15.157
I HIT MY BACK.

855
00:42:15.201 --> 00:42:16.724
IT REALLY HURTS.

856
00:42:16.768 --> 00:42:18.987
WE GOT TO GET ALLIE
TO A HOSPITAL.


857
00:42:19.031 --> 00:42:20.554
WE'LL NEVER MAKE IT
IN THIS STORM.


858
00:42:20.598 --> 00:42:22.904
RICK, PLEASE,
THE COAST IS DEADLY.


859
00:42:22.948 --> 00:42:25.211
WE'VE GOT TO MOVE
AWAY FROM LAND,
NOT CLOSER IN.


860
00:42:25.254 --> 00:42:26.516
