MY LAST POSITION.
MY MISTAKE.


883
00:43:22.050 --> 00:43:23.922
I FEEL HORRIBLE
ABOUT ALLIE.


884
00:43:23.965 --> 00:43:25.924
AW, SHE SHOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN UP HERE.


885
00:43:25.967 --> 00:43:27.534
SHE WOULDN'T
HAVE BEEN UP HERE
IF IT WASN'T FOR ME.


886
00:43:27.577 --> 00:43:29.144
I WAS YELLING AT HER
FOR NOT HELPING OUT.


887
00:43:29.188 --> 00:43:30.842
IT'S MY FAULT.

888
00:43:30.885 --> 00:43:33.279
ALL RIGHT!

889
00:43:33.322 --> 00:43:36.804
THE COAST GUARD
SAYS SAN SIMEON'S
OUR CLOSEST DOCK.


890
00:43:36.848 --> 00:43:39.546
RICK WANTS US
TO CHANGE THE HEADING
TO 300 DEGREES.


891
00:43:39.589 --> 00:43:40.895
THAT'S A BAD IDEA,
MATT.


892
00:43:40.939 --> 00:43:41.983
WE'LL BE BROADSIDE
TO THE WAVES.


893
00:43:42.027 --> 00:43:43.071
WE'LL RISK...

894
00:43:43.115 --> 00:43:45.030
NOBODY ASKED YOU.
JUST DO IT, SUSAN.


895
00:43:45.073 --> 00:43:46.509
MATT, WE'RE
GONNA BE SWAMPED.


896
00:43:46.553 --> 00:43:47.641
MATT, YOU'RE
NOT THINKING.


897
00:43:47.685 --> 00:43:48.773
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE SAY...


898
00:43:48.816 --> 00:43:50.035
CHANGE COURSE NOW!

899
00:43:50.078 --> 00:43:51.950
NO, I WON'T.
IT'S SUICIDE!


900
00:43:58.870 --> 00:44:01.263
MY GOD, MATT,
YOU'RE JEOPARDIZING
ALL OF OUR LIVES!


901
00:44:01.307 --> 00:44:04.005
YOU'RE BOTH
RELIEVED OF YOUR DUTIES
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY!


902
00:44:04.049 --> 00:44:05.746
YOU AND RICK
CAN'T HANDLE
THIS BOAT


903
00:44:05.790 --> 00:44:06.834
BY YOURSELVES
IN THIS STORM.


904
00:44:06.878 --> 00:44:08.009
AW, FORGET IT.

905
00:44:08.053 --> 00:44:10.185
HE'D RATHER
KILL US ALL
THAN LOOK WEAK.


906
00:44:10.229 --> 00:44:12.274
IF YOU DON'T GET
DOWN BELOW, I'LL
DRAG YOU DOWN MYSELF!


907
00:44:12.318 --> 00:44:14.929
NO. NO. I AM STAYING
HERE TO HELP...


908
00:44:14.973 --> 00:44:18.411
MATT, STOP IT... AAH!

909
00:44:18.454 --> 00:44:20.282
JASON!

910
00:44:20.326 --> 00:44:23.024
JASON! OH! NO!

911
00:44:23.068 --> 00:44:24.417
NO, JASON!

912
00:44:24.460 --> 00:44:26.245
JASON!

913
00:44:28.726 --> 00:44:29.596
Susan: THAT'S ENOUGH.

914
00:44:29.639 --> 00:44:31.250
STOP IT!

915
00:44:36.081 --> 00:44:37.691
JASON!

916
00:44:37.735 --> 00:44:38.910
JASON!

917
00:44:38.953 --> 00:44:42.087
AAH!

918
00:44:42.130 --> 00:44:44.089
JASON!

919
00:44:44.132 --> 00:44:45.307
JASON!

920
00:44:45.351 --> 00:44:46.918
WHAT HAPPENED?

921
00:44:46.961 --> 00:44:48.441
I DIDN'T MEAN TO.

922
00:44:50.704 --> 00:44:52.358
WHAT HAPPENED,
SUSAN?


923
00:44:52.401 --> 00:44:54.664
THEY HAD A FIGHT.
JASON WENT OVER.


924
00:44:54.708 --> 00:44:55.709
JASON!

925
00:44:55.753 --> 00:44:57.406
JASON!

926
00:44:57.450 --> 00:45:00.670
JASON!
JASON!


927
00:45:00.714 --> 00:45:01.628
WHERE IS HE?

928
00:45:01.671 --> 00:45:03.369
SUSAN,
IT'S TOO LATE.


929
00:45:03.412 --> 00:45:04.631
